Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊拉 龍捲風的裡面……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有條龍……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它移動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎 快到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛兵……沒有衛兵在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著王宮去了……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
